videos.headline: LSU strikes first with 1-yard TD run
videos.description: Nick Brossette shoots through a hole and finds the end zone to give the Tigers an early 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: LSU doubles lead on first play of 2nd quarter
videos.description: Nick Brossette follows his blockers and gets across the goal line for his second rushing touchdown of the first half, making it 14-0 Tigers.

videos.headline: LSU makes INT and scores TD on next play
videos.description: DB Ed Paris picks off J'Mar Smith on a batted ball, and then Clyde Edwards-Helaire wastes no time in converting it to a 28-yard touchdown to make it 24-0 Tigers.

videos.headline: Louisiana Tech gets on board with 20-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB J'Mar Smith throws off his back foot and connects with WR Adrian Hardy, who fights to the goal line and cuts the LSU lead to 24-7.

videos.headline: Louisiana Tech converts on 4th-and-goal for 1-yard TD
videos.description: QB J'Mar Smith finds WR Bobby Holly in the flat and brings the Bulldogs to within 10 of the Tigers.

videos.headline: Louisiana Tech narrows lead with 42-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB J'Mar Smith squeezes it between two defenders and connects with WR Adrian Hardy in the end zone, shrinking LSU's lead to 24-21.

videos.headline: LSU pads lead with 2-yard TD
videos.description: Nick Brossette powers his way into the end zone, extending the Tigers' lead to 31-21 over the Bulldogs.

videos.headline: LSU puts game away with 1-yard TD run
videos.description: RB Clyde Edwards-Helaire punches it into the end zone to make it 38-21 Tigers and put the game on ice.
